comment._content: Douglas YA3D-1 Skywarrior. Bu No 130352 Side code 352. Midnight blue paint scheme overall YA3D-1 130352 Accepted Oct 1953 Became NA-3A from 1962. Struck off Charge at NARF Alameda following June 1965 inflight accident while operated by Naval Missile Center from Point Mugu, California. Possibly SOC April 1966. As yet there is no record of the incident here: www.a3skywarrior.com/memorial/full_accident_date.htm
